You just have to re-place the old maps with this.
And it runs very smooth :-)

Thanks for posting this, installed on my Chinese Head Unit yesterday With Primo 2.2 found here 
" http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7097220/iGO_Primo_2.2_International_Edition_by_Zervdim_Greece " and wow this is absolutely Brilliant. I used the Tomsoft skin and it Looks and works so much better than IGO8 & Primo 1.2 ever did. The extra options alone and the increased quality of my TMC are without doubt brilliant unexpected extras.

I Highly Recommend this to any one running the Chinese Wince Head units with Sat/Nav it's like installing a brand new Unit.

The PirateBay Torrents are Fine, Fast, Safe Torrents and I will continue Seeding to help keep them Alive.
